headline.main: No. 7 Arizona Pulls Away to Beat Arizona State 73-60
headline.print_headline: No. 7 Arizona Pulls Away to Beat Arizona State 73-60

lead_paragraph: Arizona played two months without its top returning player, suffered through a slew of injuries and lost an emotional final home game.
